k\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/UH2QV5OALNB73HD25ODE4IMZXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民促派兩萬 陳茂波：有分歧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mraAYSeHM2S7Xt9uQQYWyJohdBg=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NIYFDIT6DRCBDAKDZRRCUJ2BS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmraAYSeHM2S7Xt9uQQYWyJohdBg%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNIYFDIT6DRCBDAKDZRRCUJ2BS4.jpg&h=77c9ed5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳茂波<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】財政司司長陳茂波下月底將公佈財政預算案，有市民昨向陳茂波建議可提前提取四分之一至三分之一強積金在疫情下應急，但陳茂波拒絕，指強積金原意是希望市民退休時有保障，「如果因面對短期困難而拆鬆，政府會有擔心」，寧從其他方面想辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預算案無意撤辣或推租管<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波昨日出席港台節目《眾言堂》聽取市民對預算案的建議，市民提出多項訴求，但陳茂波非即時拒絕，便是顧左右而言他。有聽眾提出預算案全民派兩萬元，陳茂波竟指社會對「派錢」意見有分歧，政府需要綜合平衡。<br />\n<br />\n面對樓價飆升，不少市民只能。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有市民擔心本港人口老化問題。。。。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"分歧係一批叫派一百萬、一批叫派兩萬！"},{"pid":"1f884b5ad43429d1d647bb2494fb54eaba974073","tid":2361392,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"949968c6094121532e06d63ffc05f2d0736dd9dd","tid":2361392,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"向年薪10萬以上高級公務員及垃圾會議員徵收150%薪俸稅，以體現共渡時艱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"係徵收去年薪金總和的150%作為薪俸稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32ab40f0ba64c76bb075adc995f7672c40eab9f","tid":2361392,"uid":227177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"某波:加稅收到，派錢有分歧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f3b4716ebe6ec612c6e4c54260beb624819299","tid":2361392,"uid":370479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:30:52.000Z